<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Option 2: Collapsible Sidebar (Minimalistic)</title>
  <style>
    /* Very basic reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: sans-serif; /* More generic font */
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      /* Removed color, inherit from parent */
    }

    .sidebar {
      width: 50px; /* Slightly smaller collapsed width */
      /* Removed background and border, inherit */
      padding-top: 10px; /* Less padding */
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sidebar.expanded {
      width: 200px; /* Slightly smaller expanded width */
    }

    .toggle-btn {
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px; /* Less margin */
      transition: all 0.2s; /* Faster transition */
    }

    /* Hover effect */
    .toggle-btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .toggle-btn img {
      max-width: 40px; /* Smaller logo */
      height: auto;
      display: block; /* For consistent spacing */
      margin: 0 auto; /* Center the logo */
    }

    .sidebar.expanded .toggle-btn img {
      max-width: 60px; /* Smaller expanded logo */
    }

     /* TPA Home Text - only visible when expanded */
    .tpa-home-text {
      display: none; /* Hidden by default */
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .sidebar.expanded .tpa-home-text{
      display: block;
    }

    .menu {
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 0 15px; /* Less padding */
    }

    .sidebar.expanded .menu {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .menu ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0; /* Remove default padding */
    }

    .menu ul li {
      margin: 10px 0; /* Less margin */
    }

    .menu ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      /* Removed color and font-weight, inherit */
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
      display: block; /* Make the whole area clickable */
      padding: 5px; /* Add some padding for better click target */
    }

    /* Removed hover color, inherit or use a subtle effect */
    .menu ul li a:hover {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); /* Very subtle hover */
    }

    .content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Removed specific styles for content, inherit */

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <div class="toggle-btn" id="toggleBtn">
      <a href="https://thepocusatlas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="../images/vexus-ai-logo.png" alt="Vexus-AI: Go to TPA Home" />
      </a>
      <span class="tpa-home-text">TPA Home</span>
    </div>
    <div class="menu">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 1</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 3</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h1>Option 2: Collapsible Sidebar (Minimalistic)</h1>
    <p>
      This is a refined version of the collapsible sidebar. It's designed to be even more minimalistic and less likely to conflict with existing styles.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Vexus-AI logo is smaller and serves as the primary visual cue.  When expanded, "TPA Home" text appears below the logo for clarity.
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
    const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar');
    const toggleBtn = document.getElementById('toggleBtn');

    toggleBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      sidebar.classList.toggle('expanded');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
